<plot>A young Dutch woman settles in an Israeli kibbutz after having traveled around the world. She encountered suffering and loneliness everywhere, and she now clutches on to the values of collective involvement as the only way of life she wants to live. She is cast to play the role of the biblical character of Ruth in a film produced by a kibbutz member. She uses her own life experiences in her performance.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?180428</url></doc>
